title: [Necropolis, Narthex]
description: A headless humanoid statue sits on a throne atop a raised rostrum against the western wall.  Spiderwebs completely cover the statue, obfuscating its intended identity.  Cradled in the mass of webbing of the outstretched left hand is a severed head, which still looks fairly fresh.
paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, east, southeast
